OL,3,CCrunch time for carrots and potatoes
OL,4,Cas dry conditions jeopardise harvest
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Sarah Lock
OL,8,FCarrots and potatoes could see price
OL,9,Frises this year if the UK continues to
OL,10,Fexperience unseasonably dry
OL,11,Fconditions, the British Growers
OL,12,FAssociation has warned.
OL,14,FIt comes after a disastrous pea
OL,15,Fharvest, where hot and dry weather
OL,16,Fcaused peas to harvest early, but with
OL,17,Flow yields compared to recent years.
OL,19,FBut just how at risk could your Sunday
OL,20,Froast be?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
