OL,3,CCrunch time for carrots and potatoes
OL,4,Cas dry conditions jeopardise harvest
OL,6,FFarmers rooting for some rain
OL,8,FFarmers were plagued with an
OL,9,Funseasonably wet growing season last
OL,10,Fyear, disrupting their ability to
OL,11,Fplant seeds, and swamping crops.
OL,13,FThe spring of 2025, in contrast, has
OL,14,Fbeen the warmest and sunniest on
OL,15,Frecord.
OL,17,F"This year is one of the best springs
OL,18,Fin living memory for getting seeds in
OL,19,Fthe ground," explains John Walgate,
OL,20,FChief Executive at the British Growers
OL,21,FAssociation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
