OL,4,Cas dry conditions jeopardise harvest
OL,6,FThere would usually be around nine
OL,7,Fpeas in a pod on average, but now
OL,8,Ffarmers were getting only two. For
OL,9,Fsome, it became uneconomic to even try
OL,10,Fharvesting them.
OL,12,FThe concern now is that this dry
OL,13,Fweather will continue, affecting the
OL,14,Fwinter root vegetables.
OL,16,F"It's probably too early to tell for
OL,17,Fcarrots, potatoes and onions,"
OL,18,Fexplains John.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
