OL,6,F"A lot of the crops are irrigated, so
OL,7,Fthey've been ok up until now. But once
OL,8,Fa farmer uses their on-farm reservoir,
OL,9,Fit's not getting replenished.
OL,11,F"The critical time is going to be the
OL,12,Fnext eight weeks. If there is no rain,
OL,13,Fwe're going to have poor yields."
OL,15,FAnd it needs to be a decent amount of
OL,16,Frain. Even the deluge that Storm
OL,17,FFloris brought wasn't enough to save
OL,18,Fthe peas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
