OL,6,FBad news for brassicas too. Those
OL,7,Fgrown on the eastern side of England
OL,8,Fhave been affected by the dry weather,
OL,9,Fand the supply of cauliflowers is
OL,10,Fexpected to be down.
OL,12,F"I don't think consumers will see
OL,13,Fempty shelves. What you may see is
OL,14,Fmore imported products, which could
OL,15,Flead to products being more
OL,16,Fexpensive," explains John.
