OL,6,F2025 has seen the driest six months to
OL,7,FJuly in almost 50 years. Five areas of
OL,8,FEngland are in drought, while six more
OL,9,Fare at risk, after experiencing
OL,10,Fprolonged dry weather.
OL,12,FThe national drought group warned that
OL,13,FEngland is seeing widespread
OL,14,Fenvironmental and agricultural impacts
OL,15,Ffrom the lack of water. It not only
OL,16,Faffects crop yields, but also reduces
OL,17,Ffeed for livestock, damages wetlands
OL,18,Fand river wildlife, and increases the
OL,19,Frisk of wildfire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
