OL,6,FMore than 80% of farmers have said
OL,7,Fextreme weather has hit their
OL,8,Fproductivity within the past five
OL,9,Fyears, according to research released
OL,10,Fby the Energy and Climate Intelligence
OL,11,FUnit in July.
OL,13,FLower yields can equal price rises, as
OL,14,Fretailers have to import produce to
OL,15,Fkeep themselves stocked.
OL,17,FNational Farmers Union Vice-President,
OL,18,FRachel Hallos warned on Tuesday that
OL,19,Fthis year's dry conditions could be
OL,20,Fruinous for some farmers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
