OL,4,Cas dry conditions jeopardise harvest
OL,6,F"Some farms are reporting a
OL,7,Fsignificant drop in yields, which is
OL,8,Ffinancially devastating for the farm
OL,9,Fbusiness and could have impacts for
OL,10,Fthe UK's overall harvest.
OL,12,F"Farming is a long-term industry and
OL,13,Fthere is growing concern about the
OL,14,Fmonths ahead.
OL,16,F"Minimal grass growth means many
OL,17,Flivestock farmers are already tapping
OL,18,Finto winter feed stocks, raising the
OL,19,Frisk of higher production costs later
OL,20,Fin the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
