OL,6,F"To avoid the swing between extreme
OL,7,Fdrought and flooding and to secure
OL,8,Fwater supplies for food production, we
OL,9,Furgently need investment in water
OL,10,Finfrastructure and a more effective
OL,11,Fplanning system.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FJohn Walgate says the increasing
OL,19,Fextreme weather events could lead to
OL,20,Ffarmers taking less risks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
