OL,6,F"Farmers are very pragmatic. Who knows
OL,7,Fwhat we're going to see next year?
OL,8,FIt's more about the extreme weather
OL,9,Fevents we're getting.
OL,11,F"I would comfortably say, there will
OL,12,Fbe less vegetables grown in the next
OL,13,Fyear. Growers will look at it on a
OL,14,Frisk and return basis."
OL,16,FHe also points out that support for
OL,17,Fgrowers has been removed - "From our
OL,18,Fpoint of view, the only sector-
OL,19,Fspecific government support has been a
OL,20,Fscheme called the Fruit and Vegetable
OL,21,FAid scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
