OL,4,Cas dry conditions jeopardise harvest
OL,6,F"That's ending this year, and it's not
OL,7,Fbeing replaced. That's rubbing salt
OL,8,Finto the wounds.
OL,10,F"It provided over 40 million a year in
OL,11,Fgovernment support, specifically for
OL,12,Fthe fruit and vegetable sector.
OL,14,F"We need to be able to hold more water
OL,15,Fin the winter to use in the summer.
OL,16,FThat comes down to making it easier
OL,17,Fand more supported for farmers to put
OL,18,Fit in place."
OL,20,FNot all doom and gloom - we're flush
OL,21,Fwith fruit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
