OL,6,FIt's been a great year for fruit and
OL,7,Ftomatoes. The mild weather in early
OL,8,Fspring meant some crops were ready
OL,9,Fearly, and continued sunshine has seen
OL,10,Fgrowers record great produce in size,
OL,11,Fyield and flavour.
OL,13,FThe UK plum industry announced a
OL,14,Fbumper crop at the start of August,
OL,15,Fand has begun to pull out of a
OL,16,F"decades-long decline"
OL,18,FBritish Apples & Pears also predicts
OL,19,Fthat 2025 could be the best year for
OL,20,Fquality and flavour, despite the dry
OL,21,Fweather.
