OL,6,FThe organisation, which represents
OL,7,FBritish apple and pear growers, said
OL,8,Fthe vast majority of orchard trees are
OL,9,Fholding up well.
OL,11,FIn early August, Ali Capper, the
OL,12,Forganisation's chair, said: "There is
OL,13,Fstill time for the weather to affect
OL,14,Fthe size of the fruit.
OL,16,F"Substantial rainfall will likely
OL,17,Fincrease the size, while dry
OL,18,Fconditions will likely mean smaller
OL,19,Ffruit.
